data.title: Matt McDonough
meta_keywords: The National Wrestling Hall Of Fame
data.meta_description: The National Wrestling Hall Of Fame
data.text:
Three-time state and conference champion and four-year honor roll student for Linn-Mar High School in Marion, Iowa.

Set school records for most takedowns in a season and tied school record for most pins in a season.

Career record of 151-15, ranking second in school history for career wins.

Four-time all-conference and all-metro selection, three-time academic all-state and two-time honorable mention ASICS All-American.
